# Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 03/08/2025

Coordy PO Assistant is a Google Sheets add-on that helps users manage vendors and purchase orders. We value your privacy and do not collect or store any personal information.

## Data Collection
- We do not collect, store, or share your personal data.
- All data processed by the add-on remains within your Google Sheets and your Google Account.

## Google Permissions
The add-on uses the following permissions:
- `Spreadsheet scope`: To read and modify the spreadsheet you're working on.

## Third Parties
We do not share your data with any third-party services.

